high_descs: Move to the stove on your left.
Take the mug out over the cabinet above the stove, right of the microwave.
Bring the mug to the microwave on the left.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the heated mug to the coffee machine on the counter to the right.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Take the coffee mug out of the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
Heat the mug in the micrwoave.
Turn right and walk past the sink to the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Go left and face the cabinet to the right of the microwave.
Take the mug out of the cabinet to the right of the microwave and shut the door.
Move to the left and face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out again.
Go right and then turn to the left to face the coffee maker on the counter.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug under a coffee maker.
